---

<div class="journey-section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2 class="section-title-glow">LỰA CHỌN HÀNH TRÌNH HỌC TẬP</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Bắt đầu hành trình chinh phục Kỹ thuật Dữ liệu (Data Engineering) theo lộ trình phù hợp với bạn.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="journey-grid">
    <!-- Card 1: Learning Paths -->
    <a href="/learning-paths/overview/" class="journey-card path-card">
      <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="card-icon">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
          <polygon points="16.24 7.76 14.12 14.12 7.76 16.24 9.88 9.88 16.24 7.76"></polygon>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <h3>Lộ trình học (Learning Paths)</h3>
        <p>Bản đồ học tập cá nhân hóa được thiết kế chuyên biệt từ con số 0 (Beginner) cho tới các hướng chuyên sâu như Analytics, Cloud, Streaming, hay Senior Engineer.</p>
        <span class="card-action">Khám phá lộ trình <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="arrow"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg></span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- Card 2: Handbook -->
    <a href="#concepts" class="journey-card concept-card">
      <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="card-icon">
          <path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20"></path>
          <path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <h3>Kiến thức cốt lõi (Handbook)</h3>
        <p>Tra cứu hệ thống hóa 6 cột trụ chính của DE: từ Cơ sở & Kiến trúc, Lưu trữ & Quản lý, Tích hợp, Xử lý Realtime, Quản trị cho tới AI & Machine Learning.</p>
        <span class="card-action">Tra cứu cẩm nang <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="arrow"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg></span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- Card 3: E2E Projects -->
    <a href="/projects/aws-e2e-project/" class="journey-card project-card">
      <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="card-icon">
          <path d="M22 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5l2 3h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
          <polygon points="12 11 12 17 17 14 12 11"></polygon>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <h3>Dự án thực chiến (E2E Projects)</h3>
        <p>Xây dựng hệ thống Data Platform hoàn chỉnh từ đầu đến cuối (End-to-End) chạy trên các đám mây lớn AWS, Azure và GCP với dbt, Airflow, Spark và Terraform.</p>
        <span class="card-action">Xem dự án thực hành <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="arrow"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg></span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- Card 4: Career Prep -->
    <a href="#career-prep" class="journey-card career-card">
      <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="card-icon">
          <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="7"></circle>
          <polyline points="8.21 13.89 7 23 12 20 17 23 15.79 13.88"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <h3>Bệ phóng sự nghiệp (Career Prep)</h3>
        <p>Luyện thi chứng chỉ Databricks Associate/Professional trực tuyến với lời giải thích chi tiết cùng kho câu hỏi phỏng vấn chuẩn hóa tuyển dụng thực tế.</p>
        <span class="card-action">Bắt đầu ôn luyện <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="arrow"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg></span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .journey-section {
    margin: 3rem 0;
    font-family: var(--sl-font), sans-serif;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .section-title-glow {
    font-size: 1.5rem !important;
    font-weight: 800 !important;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0 !important;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--sl-color-white) 30%, var(--sl-color-accent-high) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto !important;
  }

  .journey-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .journey-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* Premium Glassmorphic Cards */
  .journey-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(var(--sl-color-bg-nav-rgb, 20, 24, 33), 0.4);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-hairline);
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    color: var(--sl-color-text) !important;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Decorative card background glow on hover */
  .journey-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(800px circle at var(--x, 0px) var(--y, 0px), rgba(var(--sl-color-accent-rgb), 0.08), transparent 40%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .journey-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .journey-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(var(--sl-color-accent-rgb), 0.6);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 
                0 0 15px -3px rgba(var(--sl-color-accent-rgb), 0.15);
  }

  .card-icon-wrapper {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(var(--sl-color-accent-rgb), 0.1);
    color: var(--sl-color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--sl-color-accent-rgb), 0.15);
  }

  .journey-card:hover .card-icon-wrapper {
    background: var(--sl-color-accent);
    color: var(--sl-color-text-invert);
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(var(--sl-color-accent-rgb), 0.3);
  }

  .card-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .card-content h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0 !important;
    font-size: 1.15rem !important;
    font-weight: 700 !important;
    color: var(--sl-color-white) !important;
  }

  .card-content p {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0 !important;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .card-action {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sl-color-accent);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .arrow {
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .journey-card:hover .card-action {
    color: var(--sl-color-accent-high);
  }

  .journey-card:hover .arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Dynamic glow tracking cursor for card hover
  const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.journey-card');
  cards.forEach(card => {
    card.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
      const rect = card.getBoundingClientRect();
      const x = (e as MouseEvent).clientX - rect.left;
      const y = (e as MouseEvent).clientX - rect.top; // wait, clientY not clientX for y
      (card as HTMLElement).style.setProperty('--x', `${x}px`);
      (card as HTMLElement).style.setProperty('--y', `${(e as MouseEvent).clientY - rect.top}px`);
    });
  });
</script>
